  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">spiritual life which is the effect of charity , whereby God dwells in us. Wherefore any sin which by its very nature is contrary to charity is a mortal sin by reason of its genus. And such is sloth, because the proper effect of charity is joy in God , as stated above ( II-II:28:1 ), while sloth is</data>
