  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q008.a007.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">Two things are contained in the sixth beatitude, as also in the others, one by way of merit , viz. cleanness of heart; the other by way of reward, viz. the sight of God , as stated above ( I-II:69:2 ; I-II:6</data>
