  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q001.a009.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that it is unsuitable for the articles of faith to be embodied in a symbol. Because Holy Writ is the rule of faith , to which no addition or subtraction can lawfully be made, since it is written ( Deuterono</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q001" target="st.ii-ii.q001.a010" id="structural.st.ii-ii.q001.contains.st.ii-ii.q001.a010">
  <data key="d6">structural.st.ii-ii.q001.contains.st.ii-ii.q001.a010</data>
  <data key="d7">st.ii-ii.q001</data>
