  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q001.a010.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that it does not belong to the Sovereign Pontiff to draw up a symbol of faith . For a new edition of the symbol becomes necessary in order to explain the articles of faith , as stated above ( Article 9 ). N</data>
