  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">Outward actions belong properly to the virtue to whose end they are specifically referred: thus fasting is referred specifically to the end of abstinence, which is to tame the flesh, and consequently it is an act of abstinence. Now confession of those things t</data>
