  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">ce, which is to tame the flesh, and consequently it is an act of abstinence. Now confession of those things that are of faith is referred specifically as to its end, to that which concerns faith , according to 2 Corinthians 4:13 : "Having the same spirit of faith . . . we believe , an</data>
