  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q004.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the Apostle gives an unfitting definition of faith ( Hebrews 11:1 ) when he says: " Faith is the substance of things to be hoped for, the evidence of things that appear not." For no quality is a substa</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
