  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q014.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the sin against the Holy Ghost is not the same as the sin committed through certain malice. Because the sin against the Holy Ghost is the sin of blasphemy , according to Matthew 12:32 . But not every s</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
