  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the sin against the Holy Ghost can be forgiven. For Augustine says (De Verb. Dom., Serm. lxxi): "We should despair of no man , so long as Our Lord's patience brings him back to repentance." But if any </data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
