  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q014.a004.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that a man cannot sin first of all against the Holy Ghost , without having previously committed other sins . For the natural order requires that one should be moved to perfection from imperfection. This is </data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
