  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q020.a003.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that despair is not the greatest of sins . For there can be despair without unbelief, as stated above ( Article 2 ). But unbelief is the greatest of sins because it overthrows the foundation of the spiritua</data>
