  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that despair does not arise from sloth. Because different causes do not give rise to one same effect. Now despair of the future life arises from lust , according to Gregory (Moral. xxxi, 45). Therefore it d</data>
