  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">especially servile fear, which looks at the punishment arising from God's justice , the remission of which presumption hopes for; yet by a kind of false likeness it is more opposed to hope , since it denotes an inordinate hope in God . And since things are more directly opposed when</data>
