  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q022.a001.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that no precept should be given relating to the virtue of hope. For when an effect is sufficiently procured by one cause , there is no need to induce it by another. Now man is sufficiently induced by his na</data>
