  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q023.a008.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that charity is not the true form of the virtues . Because the form of a thing is either exemplar or essential . Now charity is not the exemplar form of the other virtues , since it would follow that the ot</data>
