  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that the love of charity stops at God and does not extend to our neighbor. For as we owe God love, so do we owe Him fear, according Deuteronomy 10:12 : "And now Israel , what doth the Lord thy God require o</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
