  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q026.a007.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that we ought to love those who are better more than those who are more closely united to us. For that which is in no way hateful seems more lovable than that which is hateful for some reason: just as a thi</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
