  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that we ought not to love more those who are more closely united to us by ties of blood. For it is written ( Proverbs 18:24 ): "A man amiable in society, shall be more friendly than a brother." Again, Valer</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q026" target="st.ii-ii.q026.a009" id="structural.st.ii-ii.q026.contains.st.ii-ii.q026.a009">
