  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q030.a004.obj1</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that mercy is the greatest of the virtues . For the worship of God seems a most virtuous act. But mercy is preferred before the worship of God , according to Hosea 6:6 and Matthew 12:7 : "I have desired mer</data>
  <data key="d18">structural</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q031" target="concept.beneficence" id="edge.st.ii-ii.q031.treated_in.concept.beneficence">
