  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q037.a001.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">Discord is opposed to concord. Now, as stated above ( II-II:29:3 ) concord results from charity , in as much as charity directs many hearts together to one thing, which is chiefly the Divine good , secondarily, the good of our neighbor. Wherefore discord</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
