  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">It would seem that strife is not a daughter of anger . For it is written ( James 4:1 ): "Whence are wars and contentions? Are they not . . . from your concupiscences , which war in your members?" But anger is not in the </data>
