  <data key="d17">It would seem that scandal is not a sin . For sins do not occur from necessity , since all sin is voluntary , as stated above ( I-II:74:1 and I-II:74:2 ). Now it is written ( Matthew 18:7 ): "It must needs be that scanda</data>
